  "text": "Yang et al. [CITATION_1] introduced an auxiliary dense character detection task to encourage the learning of visual representations that are favorable to the text patterns.And they adopted an alignment loss to regularize the estimated attention at each time-step. Further, they use a coordinate map as a second input to enforce spatial-awareness.",
